data.description: No steps, one level living at its best!! Like new rambler in the desirable Lost River development of Horace with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, custom kitchen and gas fireplace. Custom designed throughout with no detail overlooked! All the doors are wheel chair accessible. The garage is an extension of the home with epoxy floors, in floor heat, overhead door to the backyard, additional attic storage with built in elevator, hot and cold water, zoned sound. The yard features additional concrete parking, 12x20 storage shed, screened in patio, landscaping with edging and sprinkler system! This home boasts quality craftsmanship, functionality & Storage and no hassles but to move in and enjoy this home that lives like Brand New!
